  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115560/extras/16862393ca59d3e70f23715eccf85304.avif?t=1674693910\" width=384 height=96 /></span><br>You are a slime that fell into the deep caverns in an unknown realm; all while being watched by a metaphysical entity. Explore the many linear, diverse, and challenging regions in this precision-based platformer, and find your way towards <strong>FREEDOM</strong> and <strong>SAFETY</strong>.<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115560/extras/ae2a354901e6f06f4e798c131b450d10.avif?t=1674693910\" width=384 height=96 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Navigate</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Navigate through the 6 regions and the 60+ diverse levels. Keep pushing forward while you explore this dangerous realm.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115560/extras/db8a2ab085efd34641938d8796584bcf.poster.avif?t=1674693910\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115560/extras/db8a2ab085efd34641938d8796584bcf.webm?t=1674693910\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115560/extras/db8a2ab085efd34641938d8796584bcf.mp4?t=1674693910\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Power Up</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Gain Permanent powerups to progress further and take on brand new challenges each step you go.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115560/extras/b6f774de6cba655d7d8630e3c627c483.poster.avif?t=1674693910\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115560/extras/b6f774de6cba655d7d8630e3c627c483.webm?t=1674693910\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115560/extras/b6f774de6cba655d7d8630e3c627c483.mp4?t=1674693910\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Persevere</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Keep pushing forward every time you die. Your death is certaintly not the end, and so keep persevering towards the very end.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115560/extras/b52f8661c9da7b8a42ac236a39015bfc.poster.avif?t=1674693910\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115560/extras/b52f8661c9da7b8a42ac236a39015bfc.webm?t=1674693910\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115560/extras/b52f8661c9da7b8a42ac236a39015bfc.mp4?t=1674693910\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>Find your <strong>Freedom</strong>",
